---
// Logistics section component
---

<section id="logistics" class="section" aria-label="Logistics and transport">
  <div class="hero-grid" aria-hidden="true" style="opacity:.4"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Logistics &amp; Transport</p>
        <h2 class="display-2 silver">62-Ton Abnormal Heavy-Haul</h2>
        <p class="prose">Our specialised 62-ton abnormal road freight fleet is purpose-built to move bulk coal, chrome and oversized commodity loads across South Africa and the SADC region — with full permit compliance, escort coordination and end-to-end route management.</p>
        <p class="prose">From colliery and mine to port, smelter or feedlot, every load is dispatched under a single operational team that manages abnormal-load permits, cross-border documentation and driver scheduling as one workflow — not a hand-off between sub-contractors.</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li><span class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>62-ton abnormal heavy-haul road freight, with permit and escort coordination</li>
          <li><span class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Cross-border SADC movements with full documentation</li>
          <li><span class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Fleet management, dispatch and turnaround scheduling</li>
          <li><span class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>Weighbridge tickets, seals and chain-of-custody on every load</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal delay-1">
        <div class="map-card">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 800 600" role="img" aria-label="Map showing routes across Southern Africa" class="route-map">
            <path d="M180 220 L220 180 L260 170 L300 150 L360 140 L420 145 L480 160 L540 180 L600 200 L640 230 L660 270 L640 320 L630 370 L600 420 L560 460 L500 490 L440 510 L380 520 L320 515 L280 500 L240 470 L210 430 L190 380 L180 330 Z" fill="var(--surface)" stroke="hsla(182,78%,41%,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <g class="routes" stroke="var(--teal)" stroke-width="2" fill="none">
              <line x1="470" y1="270" x2="555" y2="360"/>
              <line x1="470" y1="270" x2="280" y2="510"/>
              <line x1="470" y1="270" x2="410" y2="200"/>
              <line x1="470" y1="270" x2="580" y2="250"/>
              <line x1="470" y1="270" x2="220" y2="290"/>
              <line x1="580" y1="250" x2="555" y2="360"/>
            </g>
            <g class="cities">
              <g><circle cx="470" cy="270" r="5" fill="var(--teal)"/><circle cx="470" cy="270" r="14" fill="hsla(182,78%,41%,0.18)" class="pulse"/><text x="482" y="260">Johannesburg</text></g>
              <g><circle cx="555" cy="360" r="5" fill="var(--teal)"/><circle cx="555" cy="360" r="14" fill="hsla(182,78%,41%,0.18)" class="pulse"/><text x="567" y="350">Durban</text></g>
              <g><circle cx="280" cy="510" r="5" fill="var(--teal)"/><circle cx="280" cy="510" r="14" fill="hsla(182,78%,41%,0.18)" class="pulse"/><text x="292" y="500">Cape Town</text></g>
              <g><circle cx="410" cy="200" r="5" fill="var(--teal)"/><circle cx="410" cy="200" r="14" fill="hsla(182,78%,41%,0.18)" class="pulse"/><text x="422" y="190">Gaborone</text></g>
              <g><circle cx="580" cy="250" r="5" fill="var(--teal)"/><circle cx="580" cy="250" r="14" fill="hsla(182,78%,41%,0.18)" class="pulse"/><text x="592" y="240">Maputo</text></g>
              <g><circle cx="220" cy="290" r="5" fill="var(--teal)"/><circle cx="220" cy="290" r="14" fill="hsla(182,78%,41%,0.18)" class="pulse"/><text x="232" y="280">Walvis Bay</text></g>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="truck-banner reveal">
      <img src="/assets/abnormal-truck.jpg" alt="Black62 62-ton abnormal heavy-haul truck on a South African highway" loading="lazy" width="1280" height="800" />
      <div class="truck-banner-overlay">
        <p class="eyebrow">Heavy Haul</p>
        <h3>Built for 62-ton abnormal loads</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
